ZH: 我们今天下午有重要的会议。
EN: We have an important meeting this afternoon.

ZH: 会议将在会议室举行。
EN: The meeting will take place in the conference room.

ZH: 请在会议开始前准时到达。
EN: Please arrive on time before the meeting starts.

ZH: 这次会议是为了讨论新的项目计划。
EN: The purpose of this meeting is to discuss the new project plan.

ZH: 会议的议程已经发送给了所有参与者。
EN: The agenda of the meeting has been sent to all participants.

ZH: 会议的主持人是公司的总经理。
EN: The host of the meeting is the general manager of the company.

ZH: 会议将持续两个小时。
EN: The meeting will last for two hours.

ZH: 请在会议期间关闭手机。
EN: Please turn off your phone during the meeting.

ZH: 会议将围绕团队的合作展开讨论。
EN: The meeting will focus on the team's collaboration.

ZH: 请在会议期间举手发言。
EN: Please raise your hand to speak during the meeting.

ZH: 今天的会议将有两部分内容。
EN: Today's meeting will have two parts of content.

ZH: 会议的地点已经确定在总部会议室。
EN: The location of the meeting has been confirmed in the headquarters conference room.

ZH: 请在会议开始前准备好所有需要的资料。
EN: Please prepare all necessary materials before the meeting starts.

ZH: 会议的目的是为了解决我们当前遇到的问题。
EN: The purpose of the meeting is to solve the problems we are facing.

ZH: 请在会议结束后提交会议记录。
EN: Please submit the meeting minutes after the meeting ends.

ZH: 会议期间请保持安静，以便其他人能够专心听讲。
EN: Please keep quiet during the meeting so that others can focus on listening.

ZH: 会议将讨论公司下一季度的销售计划。
EN: The meeting will discuss the sales plan for the next quarter.

ZH: 请在会议结束后留下来与我交流。
EN: Please stay after the meeting to talk with me.

ZH: 会议结束后我们将进行一次小组讨论。
EN: After the meeting, we will have a group discussion.

ZH: 我们已经为下周的会议做好了准备。
EN: We have prepared for the meeting next week.
